Package org.openidentityplatform.openam.click.element

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openidentityplatform.openam.click.element.Element
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResourceElement
    public class Element
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Provides a base class for rendering HTML elements, for example JavaScript (<script>) and Cascading Stylesheets (<link> / <style>).

    Subclasses should override getTag() to return a specific HTML tag.

    See Also:
